---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Now">
    <section class="now">
        <h1>What I'm Doing <span class="accent"><em>Now...</em></span></h1>
        <p class="updated"><strong>Last updated:</strong> <em>April 19th, 2026</em></p>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Enjoying 😊</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Learning about new techie stuff.</li>
                <li>Coffee! ☕</li>
                <li>Gaming... <em>(always!)</em></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Doing 🤔</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Continuing my web development journey on <a href="https://freecodecamp.org" target="_blank">freeCodeCamp</a>. <em>(Attempting to make myself more hireable per the last item on this list!)</em></li>
                <li>Maintaining and improving tools on my family's home web server project.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Reading 📖</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/221144756-the-shades-of-orthea" target="_blank"><em>The Shades of Orthea</em></a> by my fellow streaming pal <a href="https://www.thatviolinchick.com/" target="_blank">Hannah Gordon.</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Watching 📺</h2>
            <p>Listen, I watch a lot of TV shows. Like <em>a lot</em> a lot. I'm a sucker for pretty much any series that keeps my interest. So, understand that I'm a little bit of a crazy person when it comes to shows that I'm watching. Currently, I'm tuned into:</p><br>
            <ul>
                <li>The second season of Marvel's <a href="https://www.disneyplus.com/en-gb/browse/entity-85e7a914-c8e6-41db-95df-c740dc2cf1b7" target="_blank"><em>Daredevil: Born Again</em></a>, because I'm pretty much just a Marvel stan at this point!</li>
                <li>I'm also doing an epic watch/rewatch of ALL iterations of <a href="https://www.paramountplus.com/shows/star_trek/" target="_blank"><em>Star Trek</em></a>, that I'll eventually be writing reviews up per season/film on my <a href="/blog">Blog</a>! Right now I'm on the first season of the original series.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Playing 🎮</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://guildwars2.com" target="_blank"><em>Guild Wars 2</em></a>. This has sorta become my “main” MMORPG since I wanted to get into one that didn't require a subscription. Sorry <em>Warcraft</em> and <em>Final Fantasy</em> fans...</li>
                <li><a href="https://enshrouded.com" target="_blank"><em>Enshrouded</em></a>... I'm a sucker for what Steam describes as “open world survival crafting” games, and this one just might be my gold standard. And it's not even out of Early Access yet!</li>
                <li><a href="https://palia.com" target="_blank"><em>Palia</em></a>... Because you always need a cozy game.</li>
                <li>I also recently picked up <a href="https://playwindrose.com/" target="_blank"><em>Windrose</em></a> and <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3326230/Hozy/" target="_blank"><em>Hozy</em></a>, both of which I'll be testing out live on <a href="https://twitch.tv/jiggyflyjoe" target="_blank">my Twitch channel</a>!
                <li>And just a little smattering of <a href="https://www.playbalatro.com/" target="_blank"><em>Balatro</em></a> on my phone. Because it is so addictive!!!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Making 🧶</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Chaos?</li>
                <li>This newly-rebuilt website!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now-section">
            <h2>Looking Forward To 📅</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>A nap!</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <p><a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank">What is a Now page???</a></p>
    </section>
</Layout>